---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - Jake Barger Portfolio">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 via-gray-800 to-gray-700 text-white py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">About Jake</h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-6">
            Sports Design & Photography Professional
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
            Passionate about creating compelling visual content that elevates collegiate athletics. 
            Currently serving as Graphic Designer & Photographer for SJSU Athletics, with previous 
            experience at Cal Football.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Profile Photo Placeholder -->
        <div class="lg:ml-8">
          <div class="relative">
            <div class="w-full max-w-md mx-auto aspect-square bg-gray-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <div class="text-center text-gray-400">
                <svg class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto mb-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 9a3 3 0 100-6 3 3 0 000 6zm-7 9a7 7 0 1114 0H3z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
                <p class="text-sm">Professional Photo<br/>Coming Soon</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="absolute top-4 right-4 bg-primary-600 text-white px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">
              Current
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Story Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">My Story</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600">
          The journey from student intern to leading sports design professional.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">The Beginning</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
              My journey in sports design began as a student intern with SJSU Football in 2020. 
              What started as a learning opportunity quickly became a passion for creating visual 
              content that captures the energy and excitement of collegiate athletics.
            </p>
            
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Growth & Development</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
              After gaining foundational experience, I moved to Cal Football as a Graphic Designer, 
              where I developed my skills in campaign creation, recruiting materials, and 
              statistical visualizations. This role taught me the importance of consistency 
              and brand alignment in sports marketing.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Current Focus</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
              Now at SJSU Athletics, I serve as both Graphic Designer and Photographer, 
              covering 17+ sports teams. This role allows me to combine my design expertise 
              with photography skills, creating comprehensive visual packages for each program.
            </p>
            
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Philosophy</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              I believe great sports design should capture the emotion, energy, and pride 
              of athletic competition. Every graphic, poster, or photograph should tell a story 
              and connect with fans on an emotional level.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Skills & Approach -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Skills & Approach</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600">
          The tools and methodologies that drive successful sports design projects.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- Design Skills -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 21a4 4 0 01-4-4V5a2 2 0 012-2h4a2 2 0 012 2v12a4 4 0 01-4 4zM21 5a2 2 0 00-2-2h-4a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a4 4 0 004 4h4a2 2 0 002-2V5z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Design Expertise</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Proficient in Adobe Creative Suite with focus on rapid turnaround and brand consistency.</p>
          <div class="space-y-2 text-sm">
            <div class="flex justify-between">
              <span class="text-gray-700">Adobe Photoshop</span>
              <span class="text-gray-500">Expert</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between">
              <span class="text-gray-700">Adobe Illustrator</span>
              <span class="text-gray-500">Expert</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between">
              <span class="text-gray-700">Adobe InDesign</span>
              <span class="text-gray-500">Advanced</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Photography Skills -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 9a2 2 0 012-2h.93a2 2 0 001.664-.89l.812-1.22A2 2 0 0110.07 4h3.86a2 2 0 011.664.89l.812 1.22A2 2 0 0018.07 7H19a2 2 0 012 2v9a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V9z"/>
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 13a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Photography</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Specialized in sports action photography and event coverage for multiple sports.</p>
          <div class="space-y-2 text-sm">
            <div class="flex justify-between">
              <span class="text-gray-700">Action Photography</span>
              <span class="text-gray-500">Expert</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between">
              <span class="text-gray-700">Event Coverage</span>
              <span class="text-gray-500">Advanced</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between">
              <span class="text-gray-700">Photo Editing</span>
              <span class="text-gray-500">Expert</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Project Management -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Project Management</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Efficient workflow management for time-sensitive sports content and campaigns.</p>
          <div class="space-y-2 text-sm">
            <div class="flex justify-between">
              <span class="text-gray-700">Rapid Turnaround</span>
              <span class="text-gray-500">Expert</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between">
              <span class="text-gray-700">Multi-Sport Coordination</span>
              <span class="text-gray-500">Advanced</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between">
              <span class="text-gray-700">Brand Consistency</span>
              <span class="text-gray-500">Expert</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Values & Interests -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16">
        <!-- Values -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Core Values</h2>
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-primary-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Excellence in Every Detail</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Every project deserves meticulous attention to design, timing, and brand alignment.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-primary-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Collaborative Spirit</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Working closely with coaches, athletes, and marketing teams to achieve shared goals.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-primary-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Continuous Innovation</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Always exploring new techniques and approaches to stay ahead in sports design.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Interests -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Beyond Work</h2>
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Sports Enthusiasm</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Passionate fan of collegiate athletics, particularly football and basketball. This genuine love for sports drives authentic design work.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Design Trends</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Constantly studying emerging design trends, typography, and visual communication techniques to bring fresh ideas to sports marketing.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Technology</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Exploring new design software, photography equipment, and digital tools that can enhance the creative process and final output.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Community</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Active in the design community, sharing knowledge and learning from other creative professionals in the sports industry.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Call to Action -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-900 text-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Let's Create Something Great</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-8">
        Ready to bring your athletics program's visual content to the next level?
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-primary-600 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-primary-700 transition-colors">
          Get In Touch
        </a>
        <a href="/work" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 border-2 border-gray-300 text-gray-300 font-semibold rounded-lg hover:border-white hover:text-white transition-colors">
          View My Work
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>